quran[111]{c,v,t}:
  12,1,"Alif, laam, raa. ∆äen ko Aayeeje Deftere …ìanngunde nden"
  12,2,"Menen Men jippiniriinde janngeteende [e …óemngal] Aarabu, belajo'o, on haqqilay"
  12,3,"Menen Me…óen fillano maa ko …ìuri mo∆¥∆¥ude e fillayee, e kon ko Men wahayini e maa…óa ndee Alqur'aanaare, hay si woniino ado mayre, ko a jeyaa…óo e welsindii…ìe …ìen"
  12,4,"Tuma nde Yuusufu maakannoo ben makko: \"Ko onon yo baaba'en, mi yi'ii [e koy…óol] koode sappo e go'o, naange ngen kadi e lewru ndun; mi yi'ii …óin no sujjana lam"
  12,5,"[Ben makko] maaki: \"Ko an yo …ìinngel am, wata a fillano musi…ó…ìe maa …ìen koy…óol maa ngol sakko …ìe fewjane feere; pellet seytaane ko ga√±oAade …ìanngu…óo"
  12,6,"Ko wano nii Joomi maa su…ìoray maa, O anndine firo koy…ói, O timmina neema Makko on e maa…óa e …ìeynguure Yaaquuba nden, wano O timminirnoo mo e baabiraa…ìe maa …ìen …ói…óo: Ibraahiima e ishaaqa. Pellet Joomi maa ko Anndu…óo √ëee√±u…óo"
  12,7,"Gom…óii wonii e Yuusufa e musi…ó…ìe makko …ìen, taskuyeeji wonannde lanndotoo…ìe …ìen"
  12,8,"tuma nde …ìe wi'unoo: \"Pellet ko Yuusufa e neene-gooto mun on …ìuraa yi…óeede ka ben-men dii enen, enen le ko en jamaa …óuu…óu…ìe. Pellet ben-men wonii e majjere …ìanngunde"
  12,9,"Waree Yuusufa maa fero…óon mo e leydi; yeeso ben mon ngon heeranoo on, wonton …ìaawo …óum yim…ìe mo∆¥∆¥u…ìe"
  12,10,"Gooto e ma…ì…ìe wi'i: \"Wata on waru Yuusufa, weddee mo ka ni…ìe woyndu yoga e setee…ìe hoccay mo, si on laatike glloo…ìe"
  12,11,"∆Åe wi'i: \"Ko an yo ben amen, ko he…ìu-maa a hoolotaako men e fii Yuusufa? Menen le ko men laa…ìam…ìe mo reedu"
  12,12,"Accitidu-mo e amen o √±aama, o fija. Menen ko men reenoo…ìe mo"
  12,13,"O maaki: \"Min no suninay lam nde yahdoton e makko; mi…óo huli nde boyeeru ndu √±aamata-mo ka welsindi-…óon e makko"
  12,14,"∆Åe wi'i: \"Pellet si saafaandu √±aamii mo e hoore ko men jamaa …óuu…óu…ìe, haray ko men hayru…ìe"
  12,15,"Nde …ìe yahdunoo e makko, …ìe fottani ukkugol mo ka ni…ìe woyndu, Men wahayini e makko: \"Ma a yeetitoyo …ìe …óee kuu…óe ma…ì…ìe hara …ìe so'aa anndude"
  12,16,∆Åe arti ka ben ma…ì…ìe kiikii…óe hi…ìe woya
  12,17,"∆Åe wi'i: \"Ko an yo baaben amen, menen men yehii me…óen adondira, men acci Yuusufa ka kaake amen saafaandu ndun √±aami mo. A hoolotaako men non, hay si men wonii goongu…ìe"
  12,18,"∆Åe ardi e dolokke makko on hino moddi ∆¥ii∆¥am fenaande. O maaki: \"Si ko woni, wonkiiji mon …óin cu…óinanii on fiyaaku. Ko mu√±al mo∆¥∆¥al [heddanii lam]! Ko Alla woni wallitor…óo e ko sifoto…óon kon"
  12,19,"Setee…ìe ari, …ìe nuli ∆¥oogoowo ma…ì…ìe on, o jippini baagal makko ngal. O wi'i: \"Ee wel¬®-welo am! E hino paykum!\" ∆Åe suu…óiri mo keyee ma…ì…ìe. Alla non ko anndu…óo ko …ìe gollata kon"
  12,20,"∆Åe yeeyiri mo coggel fam…óungel: dirhamu-woy limotoo-koy. ∆Åe woni welsindii…ìe e fii makko"
  12,21,"Soodu…óo mo on Misra wi'ani …ìeyngu makko: \"Teddin jipporde makko. Hino gasa ka o nafa en maa jogito…óe mo …ìi…ó…óo\". Ko nii Men ho…óniri Yuusufa ka leydi fii yo Men anndin mo firo koy…ói. Alla ko foolu…óo e fiyaaku Makko on: kono ko …ìuri …óuu…óude e yim…ìe …ìen anndaa"
  12,22,"Nde o yottinoo sagatalaaku makko, Men okki mo faamu e anndal. Ko wano nii Men yo…ìirta mo∆¥∆¥inoo…ìe …ìen"
  12,23,"On [debbo] mo on woni e suudu mun …óa…ì…ìiri mo hoore-makko. O soki baafe …óen o wi'i: \"Mi heblanii-mo-ma!\" O maaki: \"Moolaare Alla! Jey…óo lam on mo∆¥∆¥inii weerde am. Si ko woni, too√±oo…ìe …ìen maletaake"
  12,24,"Gom…óii [debbo] on himmanii oon. Kanko kadi o himmanayno mo si wanaa o yi'ii hujja Joomi makko on. Ko nii [Men gerdiri] fii yo Men yiltu mo e bone e pankare. Pellet ko o jeyaa…óo e jeyaa…ìe amen la…ì…ìinaa…ìe …ìen"
  12,25,"∆Åe …ói…óo kala …ìe adondiri ka baafal, o seekiri dolokke oya on …ìaawo. ∆Åe tawi moodi makko ka baafal. [debbo] on wi'i: \"Ko hon…óum woni njo…ìdi on faalanaa…óo …ìeynguure maa nden bonki si wanaa yo soke [o leptiree] lepte muusu…óe"
  12,26,"[Yuusufu] maaki: \"Ko kanko …óa…ì…ìiri lam hoore-am\". Tawanoo…óo e yim…ìe [debbo] on seeditii: \"Si tawii dolokke mum on ko yeeso seekiraa, haray ko [debbo] on goongi, kanko [gorko] on ko jeyaa…óo e fenu…ìe …ìen"
  12,27,"Si tawii non dolokke makko on ka …ìaawo seekiraa, haray [debbo] on fenii, kanko [gorko] on ko o jeyaa…óo goongu…ìe …ìen"
  12,28,"Nde [moodi makko] yi'unoo dolokke on ko …ìaawo seekori, o wi'i: \"∆äum ko jeyaa…óum e pewje mon! Pellet pewje mon …óen ko haawnii…óe"
  12,29,"Yuusufa, …óuurno gaayi e …óum. An [debbo on], insinano junuubi(bakkaat) maa …óin; tawde pellet a jeyaama e woopu…ìe …ìen"
  12,30,"Rew…ìe …ìen ka saare wi'i: \"Debbo laam…óo on …óa…ì…ìirii kurkaadu makko ndun hoore-makko! Gom…óii giggol …ìurtirii mo. Menen dey me…óen yi'a oo [debbo] e majjere …ìanngunde"
  12,31,"Nde o nanunoo pewje ma…ì…ìe …óen, o nulani …ìe, o hebilani …ìe ngawluuji, o jonni gooto kala e ma…ì…ìe la…ìi, o wi'i: \"Yaltu e ma…ì…ìe!\". Nde …ìe yi'unoo mo, …ìe mawnini mo, …ìe hetti juu…óe ma…ì…ìe …óen, …ìe wi'i: \"Kaawee Alla! Oo wanaa …ìanndinke, oo wonaali si wanaa malaa'ikaajo teddu…óo"
  12,32,"O wi'i: \"Ko oo mo'on felir…óon lam fii mun, gom…óii mi …óa…ì…ìirii mo hoore-makko o ha…óitii. Si wonii o wa…óaali ko mi yamirta mo kon, ma o soke ma o laato jeyaa…óo e hoy…ìe …ìen"
  12,33,"O maaki: \"Joomi am, Ko kaso ngon …ìurani lam e ko …ìe noddata lam e mun kon. Si a pottinaani lam pewje ma…ì…ìe …óen, mi oo√±oto e ma…ì…ìe, mi jeyee e majju…ìe …ìen"
  12,34,"Joomi makko jaabinani mo, O firliti e makko pewje ma…ì…ìe …óen. Pellet, ko Kanko woni Nanoowo, Anndu…óo On"
  12,35,"Refti fee√±ani (rew…ìe) …ìen …ìaawo nde …ìe yi'i maandeeji …óin, ma o sok-mbo tigi haa e saa'i"
  12,36,"Sukaa…ìe …ói…óo naatidi e makko ka kaso. Go…ó…óo e ma…ì…ìe wi'i: \"Min mi hoy…óii hoore-am mi…óo siiwa sanngara\". Oya kadi wi': \"Min mi hoy…óii hoore-am mi…óo ronndii ka hoore-am cobbal, colli no √±aama e maggal\". Humpitii men firo …óin, menen men yi'ii ma jeyaa…óo e mo∆¥∆¥inoo…ìe …ìen"
  12,37,"O maaki: \"√ëaametee mo wona…óon okkoreede on aratah on si wanaa mi humpitay on firo mun ado o arde on. ∆äum mo'on ko jeyee…óum e ko Joomi am anndini lam. Min mi …óalii diina yim…ìe …ìe gom…óinaa Alla, hara kam…ìe e fii laakara ko …ìe yeddu…ìe"
  12,38,"Jokku-mi diina baabiraa…ìe am …ìen: Ibraahiima e Ishaaqa e Yaaquuba. Haananaa men nde men kafidata e Alla hay e huunde. ∆äum ko jeyaa…óum e …ìural Alla e dow amen e hoore yim…ìe …ìen; kono ko …ìuri …óuu…óude e yim…ìe …ìen …ìe yettataa"
  12,39,"Ko onon yo wondii…ìe am …ói…óo ka kaso! E ko rewetee…ói sertu…ói …ìuri mo∆¥∆¥ude, kaa ko Alla Gooto Foolu…óo on"
  12,40,"On alah e rewde gaanin Makko, si wanah in…óe …óe innu…óon …óum, onon e baabiraa…ìe mon, Alla jippinanaali …óen hujja. √ëaawoore nden alanah si wanaa Alla. O yamirii wata on rewu si wanaa Kanko. Ko …óum …óum woni diina √±ii…ìuka kan; kono ko …ìuri …óuu…óude e yim…ìe …ìen …ìe anndaa"
  12,41,"Ko onon yo wondii…ìe am …ói…óo ka kaso! Go…ó…óo e mo'on yarnay koohoo mun on sanngara; oya on, o fetee, colli …óin √±aama ka hoore makko. Fiyaaku mo lanndi…óon fii mun on √±aawaama"
  12,42,"O maakani on mo o sikke da…óay e ma…ì…ìe kam…ìe …ói…óo: \"Janto lam ka koohoojo maa on\". Seytaane yejjintini mo jantanagol koohoojo makko on. [Yuusufu] √±ii…ìiti ka kaso yoga e duu…ìi"
  12,43,"Laam…óo on wi'i: \"Min mi yi'ii (e koy…óol) na'i jee…ói…ói fay…ói, na nyaama foo∆¥u…ói jee…ói…ói …óin, e dukke jee…ói…ói kecce, e go…ó…ói goo yooru…ói. Ko onon yo dental, firtanee lam ngol koy…óol am, si on laatike firtoo…ìe koy…ói"
  12,44,"∆Åe wi'i: \"Ko jii…ìu-jaa…ìu koy…ói ! Men wonaali anndu…ìe firo koy…ói"
  12,45,"Da…óu…óo on e …ìeya …ói…óo miijitii …ìaawo dumunna o wi'i: \"Min mi humpitay on firo maggol. Nulee lam"
  12,46,"Yuusufu, an yo goongu…óo! Yeetii men fii na'i jee…ói…ói fay…ói, na nyaama foo∆¥u…ói jee…ói…ói …óin, e dukke jee…ói…ói kecce, e go…ó…ói goo yooru…ói, belajo'o mi ruttoo ka yim…ìe …ìen, belajo'o, …ìe annday"
  12,47,"O maaki: \"On remay duu…ói jee…ói…ói jokkondir…ói. Kala ko so√±u…óon, accon …óum ka dukkal(butaali) mun, si wanaa see…óa e kon ko √±aamoton"
  12,48,"Refti aroyay …ìaawo …óum, duu…ìi jee…ói…ói sa…ótu…ói, …óin (duu…ìi) no √±aama kon ko marna…óon …ói si wanaa see…óa e ko maroton [fii awdi]"
  12,49,"Refti aroya …ìaawo …óum, hitaande, ko e mayre yim…ìe …ìen to…ìetee, ko e mayre kadi …ìe hamata"
  12,50,"Laam…óo on wi'i: \"Addanee lam on\". Nde imminaa…óo on arunoo mo, o maaki: \"Rutto ka koohoojo maa on lanndo…óaa mo: Ko woni fiyaaku …ìen rew…ìe hettunoo…ìe juu…óe mun …óen? Pellet Joomi am ko anndu…óo pewje ma…ì…ìe …óen"
  12,51,"[Laam…óo on] wi'i: \"Ko hon…óum wonunoo fiyaaku mon tuma …óa…ì…ìirno…óon Yuusufa hoore-makko?\" ∆Åe wi'i: \"Moolaare Alla! Men anndiraa mo ko boni\". ∆Åeyngu laam…óo on wi'i: \"Jooni goonga kan fee√±ii. Ko min …óa…ì…ìirnoo mo hoore-makko, pellet ko o jeyaa…óo e goongu…ìe …ìen"
  12,52,"∆äum ko fii yo o anndu wonnde mi janfaaki mo ka wirnii, e wonnde Alla fewnatah pewje janfotoo…ìe …ìen"
  12,53,"Mi la…ì…ìinaa hoore-am, tawde wonkii ko heewuki yamirde bone, si wanah kin ki Joomi am yurmini. Joomi am ko Haforoowo Hinnotoo…óo"
  12,54,"Laam…óo on wi'i: \"Addanee lam mo, mi heertinana mo hoore-am\". Nde o yewtunoo mo, o wi'i: \"An on hannde ka amen, ko a jom-nokku hoolaa…óo"
  12,55,"O maaki: \"Wa…óam e hoore-ngaluuji leydi ndin: ko mi reenoowo anndu…óo"
  12,56,"Ko wano nii Men √±imnirani Yuusufa ka leydi, himo jippora e mayri nokku ka o yi…ói. Me…óen he…ìnira yurmeende Amen nden on mo Men muuyi, men yeebataa njo…ìdi mo∆¥∆¥inoo…ìe …ìen"
  12,57,Pellet ko njo…ìdi laakara ndin …ìuri mo∆¥∆¥annde …ìen gom…óim…ìe …ìe laatii gom…óu…ìe
  12,58,"Baaba-gootoo…ìe Yuusufa …ìen ari …ìe naati ka makko. O annditi …ìe, kono kam…ìe …ìe paayti mo"
  12,59,"Tuma nde o hebllannoo…ìe do≈ãlle ma…ì…ìe …óen, o maaki: \"Addanee lam musi…ó…óo mon baaba-gooto. E on yi'aali mi…óo timmina …ìetu ngun, e wonnde ko mi …ìurdo mo∆¥∆¥ude e weernoo…ìe …ìen"
  12,60,"Si on addanaali lam mo, haray …ìetu alanaa on ka am …óoo; wata on …ìado lam kadi"
  12,61,"∆Åe wi'i: \"Men …óa…ì…ìiray mo ben makko, menen ko men golloo…ìe (…óum)"
  12,62,"O maakani golloo…ìe makko …ìen: \"Wa…óee coggeeli(njigguuji) ma…ì…ìe …óin ka do≈ãlle ma…ì…ìe: belajo'o …ìe annditay …ói si …ìe ruttike ka yim…ìe ma…ì…ìe …ìen, belajo'o …ìe yiltoto"
  12,63,"Tuma nde …ìe ruttinoo ka ben ma…ì…ìe, …ìe wi'i: \"Ko an yo ben(baaba) amen, men salanaama …ìetu. neldu amen musi…ó…óo amen on, men …ìetanee. Ko men reenoo…ìe mo"
  12,64,"O maaki: \"Hara mi hooloray on e fii makko, si wanaa no mi hoolornoo on non e neene-gooto makko on ko adii? Ko Alla woni mo∆¥∆¥o reenoowo, ko Kanko …ìuri mo∆¥∆¥ude yurmetee…ìe …ìen"
  12,65,"Nde …ìe udditunoo do≈ãlle ma…ì…ìe …óen, …ìe tawi coggeeli(njigguuji) ma…ì…ìe …óin ruttaama e ma…ì…ìe. ∆Åe wi'i: \"Ko an yo ben amen, ko men …óa…ì…ìata [kadi]? ∆äii ko coggeeli amen, …ói ruttaama e amen. Me…óen jiggana yim…ìe amen, men reena musi…ó…óo amen on, men …ìeydora …ìetu ngelooba; …óum ko …ìetu newiingu"
  12,66,"O maaki: \"Mi immindintaa(neldatah) mo e moo…óon haa ∆¥ettanon mi ahadi ka Alla, wonnde on artiranay lam mo si wanaa hara on hu…ìinda\". ∆Åaawo …ìe ∆¥ettanii mo ahadi ma…ì…ìe ndin, o maaki: \"Alla e dow ko wowlu…óen kon, ko O deeno"
  12,67,"O maaki: \"Ko onon yo …ìi…ó…ìe am, wata on naatiroy e damal gootal, naatiree e dame seertu…óe. Mi dun-cantaa on e (muy…óe) Alla hay e huunde. √ëaawoore alanaa si wanaa Alla: Ko e Makko mi fawii, ko e makko kadi, yo fawo fawotoo…ìe …ìen"
  12,68,"Nde …ìe naatirnoo nokku ka ben ma…ì…ìe yamirnoo …ìe …óon, …óum wonaano no duncana …ìe [ko iwri] ka Alla si wanaa haaju wonunoo…óo e fittaandu Yaaquuba mo o gasini. Kanko on, ko o jom-ganndal ngal Men anndini mo. Kono ko …ìuri …óuu…óude e yim…ìe …ìen …ìe anndaa"
  12,69,"Nde …ìe naatunoo ka Yuusufa, o ma…ì…ìi neene-gooto makko on e makko, o maaki: \"Ko mi neene-gooto maa, wata a sunor ko …ìe huuwaynoo"
  12,70,"Tuma nde o hebilannoo …ìe do≈ãlle ma…ì…ìe …óen, o wa…ói etirgal ngal ka do≈ãngal neene-gooto makko on, refti ewnotoo…óo eewnii: \"Ko onon yo setee…ìe, Ko on wuy…ìe"
  12,71,"∆Åe fewtiti e ma…ì…ìe …ìe wi'i: \"Ko hon…óum hatti…óon"
  12,72,"∆Åe wi'i: \"Men hattike etirde laam…óo on. Hino woodani kala addu…óo ngal, do≈ãngal ngelooba, ko min woni fawtii…óo …óum"
  12,73,"∆Åe wi'i: \"Men woondirii Alla, gom…óii hi…óon anndi men araali bonnugol ka leydi, men laataaki kadi wuy…ìe"
  12,74,"∆Åe wi'i: \"Ko wonata njo…ìdi makko si tawii ko on fenoo…ìe"
  12,75,"∆Åe wi'i: \"Njo…ìdi makko: ko kala mo: […óum] tawaa ka do≈ãngal mun, haray ko kanko [tigir] woni njo…ìdi mun. Ko wano non men yo…ìitirta too√±oo…ìe …ìen"
  12,76,"[Yuusufu] fu…ó…óori do≈ãle ma…ì…ìe …óen ado do≈ãngal neene-gooto makko on; refti o yaltiniri nde ka do≈ãngal neene-gooto makko on. Ko wano non men fewjirani Yuusufa, [tawde] o hattantaano nanngude neene-gooto makko on ka sariya laam…óo on, si wanaa hara ko Alla muuyi. Me…óen …ìantana darajaaji on mo Men muuyi. No e dow kala jom-ganndal ganndo [goo]"
  12,77,"∆Åe wi'i: \"Si o wujjii, haray neene-gooto makko wujjiino ko adii\". Yuusufu mari …óum ka wonkii makko, o fe√±√±inanaali …ìe …óum. O maaki: \"Ko onon …ìuri bonnde nokku! Ko Alla …ìuri anndude ko sifoto…óon"
  12,78,"∆Åe wi'i: \"Ko an yo laam…óo on, oo no mari baabiraawo nawyu…óo oggos; ∆¥ettu gooto e amen lonto makko. Menen men yi'ii ma jeyaa…óo e mo∆¥∆¥inoo…ìe …ìen"
  12,79,"O maaki: \"Moolaara Alla nde men nanngata si wanaa on mo men tawi do≈ãlle amen …óen e juu…óe mun. Mene haray ontuma ko men too√±u…ìe"
  12,80,"Nde …ìe ta∆¥inoo fii hettugol mo, …ìe martiti ko …ìe gunndondir…ìe. Maw…óo ma…ì…ìe on wi'i: \"E on anndaa wonnde ben mon ∆¥ettodii e mo'on ahadi ka Alla, e aranun tuma welsindino…óon e Yuusufa? Mi seerataa leydi ndin haa ben am du≈ãanoo lam maa O √±aawana lam [hettugol mo], ko Kanko …ìuri mo∆¥∆¥ude e √±aawoo…ìe …ìen"
  12,81,"Ruttee ka ben mon wi'on: \"Ko an yo ben amen, …ìi…ó…óo maa on wujjii. Men seedaaki si wanaa ko men anndi, men wonaali reenu…ìe ko wirnii"
  12,82,"Lanndo (yim…ìe) saare nden nde men wonunoo e mun, e setee…ìe …ìen …ìe men hawrondirnoo e mun. Pellet ko men goongu…ìe"
  12,83,"[Yaaquuba] maaki: \"Wonkiiji mon …óin cu…óanii on fiyaake! Ko mu√±al labangal. Hino hasii ka Alla artiranta mi …ìe, …ìe denndaangal. Ko Kanko woni Anndu…óo, √ëee√±u…óo"
  12,84,"O …óuurnii …ìe o maaki: \"Ee suno am e fii Yuusufa!\" Gite makko …óen rawniri suno. Ko o suu…ó…óo suno"
  12,85,"∆Åe wi'i: \"Men woodirii Alla! A seerataa hi…óa janntoo fii Yuusufa, haa wonaa horsu…óo maa wonaa jeyaa…óo e halkii…ìe …ìen"
  12,86,"O maaki: \"Anndee ko e Alla mi wullitotoo annde am e sunaare am. Mi…óo anndi ka Alla ko on anndaa"
  12,87,"Ko onon yo …ìi…ó…ìe am, yehee tefon fii Yuusufa e neene-gooto makko on. Wata on ta∆¥o e yurmeende Alla. Ko fii, ta∆¥otaako e yurmeende Alla si wanaa yim…ìe yeddu…ìe …ìen"
  12,88,"Nde …ìe naatunoo ka makko [kanko Yuusufa], …ìe wi'i: \"Ko an yo laam…óo, lorra he…ìii men memen e …ìeynguure amen; men ardii e sil'a jaasu…óo. Hunnan men …ìetu ngun, sakko-…óaa e amen. Pellet, Alla yo…ìay sakkotoo…ìe …ìen"
  12,89,"O maaki: \"Enee, on annditii ko wa…óuno…óon Yuusufa e neene-gooto makko on kon tuma nde wonuno…óon majju…ìe"
  12,90,"∆Åe wi'i: \"Kere ko an woni Yuusufa?\" O maaki: \"Ko min woni Yuusufa. Oo …óoo ko mi√±am. Gom…óii Alla mo∆¥∆¥ike e amen. Ko fii, mo gom…óii o mu√±√±ike, pellet, Alla yeebataa njo…ìdi mo∆¥∆¥inoo…ìe …ìen"
  12,91,"∆Åe wi'i: \"Men woondiri Alla, Alla …ìurnii ma e amen, men woniino woopu…ìe"
  12,92,"O maaki: \"Feloore alaa e hoore-mon hannde! Yo Alla yawtan on. Ko Kano woni Mo∆¥∆¥o Yurmetee…óo"
  12,93,"Yahdee e oo dolokke am …óoo, werlo…óon mo ka yeeso baaben am: o wattinay yi'oowo. Addanon lam …ìeynguure mon nden …ìe denndaangal"
  12,94,"Nde setee…ìe …ìen seerti [yalti Misra]ben ma…ì…ìe maaki: \"Min mi…óo he…ìa balangol Yuusufa, sinno wanaa fii yo on …óaytinam"
  12,95,"∆Åe wi'i: \"Men woondirii Alla, an hi…óa e majjere maa…óa …ìooyunde nden"
  12,96,"Nde wewlinoowo on arunoo, o werlii [dolokke] on ka yeeso makko, o wonti yi'oowo. O maaki: \"E mi wi'anaano on mi…óo anndi ka Alla ko on anndaa"
  12,97,"∆Åe wi'i: \"Ko an yo ben amen, insinano men junuubi amen. Menen men woniino woopu…ìe"
  12,98,"O maaki: \"Armami insinano on Joomi am. Ko Kanko woni Haforoowo, Hinnotoo…óo"
  12,99,"Nde …ìe naatunoo ka Yuusufa, o weerni ka makko […óon] maw…ìe makko …ìen …ói…óo, o maaki: \"Naatiree Misra, si Alla muuyii, ko on hoolii…ìe"
  12,100,"O towniri maw…ìe makko …ìen …ói…óo ka belorki(danki), …ìe naayirani mo sujjugol. O maaki:\"Ko onon yo baaba'en, ko …óum …óoo woni firo koy…óol am ngol oya tuma, gom…óii Joomi am wa…óii ngol goonga. Gom…óii O mo∆¥∆¥ike e am tuma O yaltinnoo lam ka kaso, O itti on ka ladde, …ìaawo nde seytaane bonnii hakkunde am e ben-gootoo…ìe am …ìen. Pellet, Joomi am ko newanii…óo ko O muuyi kon. Ko Kanko woni Anndu…óo, √ëee√±u…óo"
  12,101,"Joomi am, gom…óii A ye…óii lam laamu, A anndinii lam kadi firo koy…ói. [An] Tagu…óo kammuuli …óin e leydi ndin, ko An woni gi…óo am aduna e laakara. ∆≥ettitam ko mi juul…óo, wa…óitdaa lam e mo∆¥∆¥u…ìe …ìen"
  12,102,"∆äum ko jeyaa…óum e kumpite wirnii…óe, Me…óen wahayini …óe e maa…óa. A tawanooka e ma…ì…ìe tuma nde …ìe e…ì…ìunoo fiyaaku ma…ì…ìe on hi…ìe fewja"
  12,103,"Ko …ìuri …óuu…óude e yim…ìe …ìen, hay si a rer…ói, (…ìe) wonaali gom…óinoo…ìe"
  12,104,A …óa…ì…ìiraali …ìe e …óum njo…ìdi. Nde wonaali si wanaa waaju wonannde winndere nden
  12,105,"∆äuu…óii e Aayeeje ka kammuuli e ka leydi, hi…ìe rewa e majje hara ko …ìe …óuurnii…ìe …óe"
  12,106,"Ko …ìuri …óuu…óude e ma…ì…ìe gom…óintaa Alla, si wanaa hara ko …ìe sirku…ìe"
  12,107,"E …ìe hooli nde hippooje arata …ìe e lepte Alla …óen maa darngal ngal ardira …ìe juhal, hara kam…ìe …ìe so'aa"
  12,108,"Maaku: \"Ko ngo'ol woni laawol am, mi…óo noddira e Alla dow hujja, min e …ìen jokku…ìe lam. Senayee woodanii Alla! Mi wonaali jeyaa…óo e sirkoo…ìe …ìen"
  12,109,"Men Nulaali ado maa si wanaa wor…ìe jeyaa…ìe e yim…ìe ca'e …óen, Me…óen wahayina e ma…ì…ìe. E …ìee [fennoo…ìe ma] yiilotaako ka leydi, …ìe ndaara ko honno battane …ìen adinoo…ìe …ìe wa'unoo? Pellet ko saare laakara nden …ìuri mo∆¥∆¥annde …ìen hulu…ìe [Alla]. E on haqqiltaa"
  12,110,"Haa si tawii Nulaa…ìe …ìen ta∆¥ike, (heefer…ìe …ìen) fellita wonnde kam…ìe …ìe fennaama, ballal Amen ngal ara e ma…ì…ìe; Men da…ónda on mo Men muuyi, lepte Amen …óen ruttetaake gaayi e yim…ìe bom…ìe …ìen"
  12,111,"Gom…óii wonii e fillayeeje ma…ì…ìe …óin tasakuyye wonannde joomiraa…ìe haqqillaaji …ìen. Nde wonaali yewtere fefindaande. Ko woni, ko nde goonginnde …óen adinoo…óe nde, e fensitunde kala huunde, e peewal e yurmeende wonannde yim…ìe gom…óim…ìe …ìen"